# 🌐 Local Install - Internet Access Setup

## 📋 Complete Setup Instructions for Crop-Preview System

### 🚀 Step 1: Start the Server
```bash
cd C:\Users\PC\Desktop\test
node patched-rtmp-test.js
```

**Expected Output:**
```
✅ CookiesHelper imported successfully
🚀 PATCHED RTMP Streaming Server running on http://localhost:3005
🌐 Server accessible from internet on port 3005
🎯 Pipeline: Chrome DevTools → PATCHED puppeteer-screen-recorder → RTMP
✨ NO MP4 FILES • DIRECT RTMP • PATCHED LIBRARY • REAL-TIME
🔧 Library modification: pageVideoStreamWriter.ts now supports RTMP URLs
```

### 🌐 Step 2: Create Public Internet Access (Cloudflare Tunnel)
**Open a NEW terminal window** (keep server running in first one):
```bash
cd C:\Users\PC\Desktop\test
npx cloudflared tunnel --url http://localhost:3005
```

**Expected Output:**
```
Your quick Tunnel has been created! Visit it at:
https://[random-name].trycloudflare.com
```

### 🎯 Step 3: Access Your System
**Use the provided Cloudflare URL:**
- **Main page:** `https://[your-tunnel-url].trycloudflare.com`
- **Crop Preview:** `https://[your-tunnel-url].trycloudflare.com/crop-preview.html`

### ✅ Available Features:
- **🎬 Interactive Browser Preview** - Real-time website preview
- **📐 Full Browser Window Resize** - Entire Chrome window resizing
- **📜 Enhanced Scroll Control** - Multiple scroll capture methods
- **🔴 RTMP Live Streaming** - Direct streaming to YouTube/Twitch
- **🍪 Cookie Authentication** - Login support for protected sites
- **🌐 Default URL:** https://www.aiscore.com/

### 🔧 Alternative: Localtunnel (Backup Option)
If Cloudflare doesn't work, use localtunnel:
```bash
npm install -g localtunnel
lt --port 3005
```

### 📝 Usage Instructions:
1. **Load Preview** - Click "🌐 Load Preview" button
2. **Resize Browser** - Use preset buttons (720p, 1080p, 480p, 360p)
3. **Control Scroll** - Scroll in preview or use manual X/Y controls
4. **Start Streaming** - Add RTMP URL + Stream Key, click "Start Stream"

### 🎯 RTMP Streaming Setup:
- **YouTube Live:** `rtmp://a.rtmp.youtube.com/live2/` + your stream key
- **Twitch:** `rtmp://live.twitch.tv/live/` + your stream key

### 🛠️ Troubleshooting:
- **Server not starting:** Check port 3005 is available
- **Tunnel errors:** Ensure server is running first
- **Browser not resizing:** Check console logs for errors
- **Scroll not working:** Try manual X/Y inputs

### 📊 System Requirements:
- **Node.js** - For server and tunnel
- **Chrome Browser** - For Puppeteer automation
- **Internet Connection** - For public access

---
**✨ Your crop-preview system is now accessible worldwide!**